Library Management System - Project Summary
Description:
A console-based Library Management System in Java that allows members (students and faculty) to
borrow and return books. It enforces borrowing limits based on member type.
Key Features:
- Add/View books
- Register student/faculty members
- Issue and return books
- Member-based borrowing limits
- Uses OOP concepts and Java Collections
Technologies:
- Java Core (OOP, Inheritance, Polymorphism, Encapsulation)
- ArrayList, HashMap
- Exception Handling
Structure:
- model/ : Book.java, Member.java, StudentMember.java, FacultyMember.java
- service/ : LibrarySystem.java
- Main.java : Runs the console application
Ideal for final year students and Java learners for resume enhancement.
